HEADWORD: male plug
<hw>male plug</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Electricity)</fld> <def>The
connecting end of the cord on an electrical device, having two or three
pins, that is inserted into a matching socket to make an electrical
connection.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> plug.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

